headline: Blackstone and Phoenix Financial Announce Partnership
summary: TEL AVIV, Israel & NEW YORK, December 17, 2025--Phoenix Financial ("Phoenix", TASE: PHOE), a leading Israel-based asset management and insurance company, and Blackstone (NYSE: BX), the world’s largest alternative asset manager, today announced a strategic partnership.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks with Promising Prospects and 1 We Ignore
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is home to the biggest and most well-known companies in the market, making it a go-to index for investors seeking stability. But not all large-cap stocks are created equal - some are struggling with slowing growth, declining margins, or increased competition.
